{
  "stem": "15115.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they were taking through places there were no nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at night, you used to have a rest on the grass, if somewhere was grass.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sleep without clothes, without anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was around August, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was really hot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After walking the-- I think it was about, I don't know, 30 kilometers or something-- they put us into trains.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They give us one can of meat and a half a loaf of bread, or a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was salty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The meat was salty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were dying for water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Finally, they put us into trains, wagons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, the cattle wagons has those big doors in the middle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They put us 45, one wagon on this side, and 45 on the other side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the big doors was occupied by one German and two Polish couples.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, gentiles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they put us sitting on the floor, one top of the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think it was five rows of nine on each side of the-- what do you call-- of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, there were people dying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE] killing each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As soon as we used to pass through-- what do you call-- a river to dump the bodies, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those Germans, and the kapos, they were hitting us because we were screaming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wanted to-- I don't believe it was very long that we were in the trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But from the 90 people that we got into the wagons, only about 60-65 arrived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We take at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
